      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，都需要异常处理。CloudFilter如果All cloudy就直接结束；DownloadBands和ReadRaster失败都要走到Error状态，最后统一Abort。另外查询不到数据也要直接终止。",
      "elements_involved": [
